                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout>
                           <p>Columns: 1;
                                                  ruled lines: 26;
                                                  written lines: 26; All the books except Joel, Amos, Obadiah, Jonah, Nahum, Zephaniah and Malachi begin a new page. The beginnings of the chapters according to the Christian division are marked in the margin with the letter 'samekh' and the respective number. The beginning and the end of the Hafṭarot are indicated in the margin. Masorah magna occupies one line in the upper and from one to two lines in the lower margin of each page. The number of verses is stated at the end of each book, except Zechariah and Malachi. </p>
                        </layout>
                     </layoutDesc>
